overview: Kahit akoy busabos is a 1993 Tagalog-language Action Crime film written by Ed Tuboran and Humilde 'meek' Roxas. The movie is directed by Bebong Osorio. Kahit akoy busabos stars Ace Vergel, Bing Loyzaga, Rez Cortez, Ernie David, Romy Diaz, Dexter Doria and Charles Jordan Sabalboro. It was released on 29th April 1993.
title: Kahit ako'y busabos
